         1 +  <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
         2 +  <!DOCTYPE mapper PUBLIC "-//mybatis.org//DTD Mapper 
           +  3.0//EN" "http://mybatis.org/dtd/mybatis-3-mapper.dtd">
         3 +  <mapper namespace="com.moa.dao.admin.AdminDashboardDao">
         4 +  
         5 +      <!-- 총 매출: PAYMENT_STATUS = 'COMPLETED' 인 결제 금액
           +   합계 -->
         6 +      <select id="getTotalRevenue" resultType="long">
         7 +          SELECT COALESCE(SUM(PAYMENT_AMOUNT), 0)
         8 +          FROM PAYMENT
         9 +          WHERE PAYMENT_STATUS = 'COMPLETED'
        10 +      </select>
        11 +  
        12 +      <!-- 활성 파티 수: PARTY_STATUS = 'ACTIVE' -->
        13 +      <select id="getActivePartyCount" resultType="long">
        14 +          SELECT COUNT(*)
        15 +          FROM PARTY
        16 +          WHERE PARTY_STATUS = 'ACTIVE'
        17 +      </select>
        18 +  
        19 +      <!-- 전체 파티 수 -->
        20 +      <select id="getTotalPartyCount" resultType="long">
        21 +          SELECT COUNT(*)
        22 +          FROM PARTY
        23 +      </select>
        24 +  
        25 +      <!-- 전체 유저 수 -->
        26 +      <select id="getTotalUserCount" resultType="long">
        27 +          SELECT COUNT(*)
        28 +          FROM USERS
        29 +          WHERE USER_STATUS != 'WITHDRAWN'
        30 +      </select>
        31 +  
        32 +      <!-- 오늘 가입한 회원 수 -->
        33 +      <select id="getTodayNewUsers" resultType="long">
        34 +          SELECT COUNT(*)
        35 +          FROM USERS
        36 +          WHERE DATE(REG_DATE) = CURDATE()
        37 +            AND USER_STATUS != 'WITHDRAWN'
        38 +      </select>
        39 +  
        40 +      <!-- 이번 달 매출 -->
        41 +      <select id="getThisMonthRevenue" resultType="long">
        42 +          SELECT COALESCE(SUM(PAYMENT_AMOUNT), 0)
        43 +          FROM PAYMENT
        44 +          WHERE PAYMENT_STATUS = 'COMPLETED'
        45 +            AND YEAR(PAYMENT_DATE) = YEAR(CURDATE())
        46 +            AND MONTH(PAYMENT_DATE) = MONTH(CURDATE())
        47 +      </select>
        48 +  
        49 +      <!-- 모집 중인 파티 수 -->
        50 +      <select id="getRecruitingPartyCount" resultType="long">
        51 +          SELECT COUNT(*)
        52 +          FROM PARTY
        53 +          WHERE PARTY_STATUS = 'RECRUITING'
        54 +      </select>
        55 +  
        56 +      <!-- 결제 대기 중인 건수 -->
        57 +      <select id="getPendingPaymentCount" resultType="long">
        58 +          SELECT COUNT(*)
        59 +          FROM PAYMENT
        60 +          WHERE PAYMENT_STATUS = 'PENDING'
        61 +      </select>
        62 +  
        63 +      <!-- 완료된 결제 건수 -->
        64 +      <select id="getCompletedPaymentCount" 
           + resultType="long">
        65 +          SELECT COUNT(*)
        66 +          FROM PAYMENT
        67 +          WHERE PAYMENT_STATUS = 'COMPLETED'
        68 +      </select>
        69 +  
        70 +      <!-- 이번 달 결제 건수 -->
        71 +      <select id="getThisMonthPaymentCount" 
           + resultType="long">
        72 +          SELECT COUNT(*)
        73 +          FROM PAYMENT
        74 +          WHERE PAYMENT_STATUS = 'COMPLETED'
        75 +            AND YEAR(PAYMENT_DATE) = YEAR(CURDATE())
        76 +            AND MONTH(PAYMENT_DATE) = MONTH(CURDATE())
        77 +      </select>
        78 +  
        79 +      <!-- OTT별 파티 통계 -->
        80 +      <select id="getOttPartyStats" resultType="map">
        81 +          SELECT
        82 +              pr.PRODUCT_NAME as ottName,
        83 +              COUNT(p.PARTY_ID) as partyCount,
        84 +              SUM(CASE WHEN p.PARTY_STATUS = 'ACTIVE' THEN 1 
           + ELSE 0 END) as activeCount
        85 +          FROM PRODUCT pr
        86 +          LEFT JOIN PARTY p ON pr.PRODUCT_ID = p.PRODUCT_ID
        87 +          GROUP BY pr.PRODUCT_ID, pr.PRODUCT_NAME
        88 +          ORDER BY partyCount DESC
        89 +      </select>
        90 +  
        91 +      <!-- 최근 7일 매출 -->
        92 +      <select id="getDailyRevenues" resultType="map">
        93 +          SELECT
        94 +              DATE_FORMAT(dates.date, '%Y-%m-%d') as date,
        95 +              COALESCE(SUM(p.PAYMENT_AMOUNT), 0) as amount
        96 +          FROM (
        97 +              SELECT CURDATE() as date
        98 +              UNION SELECT DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 1 
           + DAY)
        99 +              UNION SELECT DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 2 
           + DAY)
       100 +              UNION SELECT DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 3 
           + DAY)
       101 +              UNION SELECT DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 4 
           + DAY)
       102 +              UNION SELECT DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 5 
           + DAY)
       103 +              UNION SELECT DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 6 
           + DAY)
       104 +          ) dates
       105 +          LEFT JOIN PAYMENT p ON DATE(p.PAYMENT_DATE) = 
           + dates.date
       106 +              AND p.PAYMENT_STATUS = 'COMPLETED'
       107 +          GROUP BY dates.date
       108 +          ORDER BY dates.date ASC
       109 +      </select>
       110 +  
       111 +      <!-- 최근 가입 회원 (5명) -->
       112 +      <select id="getRecentUsers" resultType="map">
       113 +          SELECT
       114 +              OD_USER_ID as odUserId,
       115 +              USER_NAME as userName,
       116 +              USER_EMAIL as userEmail,
       117 +              DATE_FORMAT(REG_DATE, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') as 
           + regDate
       118 +          FROM USERS
       119 +          WHERE USER_STATUS != 'WITHDRAWN'
       120 +          ORDER BY REG_DATE DESC
       121 +          LIMIT 5
       122 +      </select>
       123 +  
       124 +      <!-- 최근 결제 내역 (5건) -->
       125 +      <select id="getRecentPayments" resultType="map">
       126 +          SELECT
       127 +              p.PAYMENT_ID as paymentId,
       128 +              p.OD_USER_ID as odUserId,
       129 +              p.PAYMENT_AMOUNT as amount,
       130 +              p.PAYMENT_STATUS as status,
       131 +              DATE_FORMAT(p.PAYMENT_DATE, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') 
           + as paymentDate,
       132 +              COALESCE(pt.PARTY_NAME, '-') as partyName
       133 +          FROM PAYMENT p
       134 +          LEFT JOIN PARTY pt ON p.PARTY_ID = pt.PARTY_ID
       135 +          ORDER BY p.PAYMENT_DATE DESC
       136 +          LIMIT 5
       137 +      </select>
       138 +  
       139 +  </mapper>

        23 +  
        24 +      private final AdminDashboardDao adminDashboardDao;
        25 +  
        26 +      @Override
        27 +      @Transactional(readOnly = true)
        28 +      public DashboardStatsResponse getDashboardStats() {
        29 +          // 기본 통계
        30 +          long totalRevenue = 
           + adminDashboardDao.getTotalRevenue();
        31 +          long activePartyCount = 
           + adminDashboardDao.getActivePartyCount();
        32 +          long totalPartyCount = 
           + adminDashboardDao.getTotalPartyCount();
        33 +          long totalUserCount = 
           + adminDashboardDao.getTotalUserCount();
        34 +  
        35 +          // 추가 통계
        36 +          long todayNewUsers = 
           + adminDashboardDao.getTodayNewUsers();
        37 +          long thisMonthRevenue = 
           + adminDashboardDao.getThisMonthRevenue();
        38 +          long recruitingPartyCount = 
           + adminDashboardDao.getRecruitingPartyCount();
        39 +          long pendingPaymentCount = 
           + adminDashboardDao.getPendingPaymentCount();
        40 +          long completedPaymentCount = 
           + adminDashboardDao.getCompletedPaymentCount();
        41 +          long thisMonthPaymentCount = 
           + adminDashboardDao.getThisMonthPaymentCount();
        42 +  
        43 +          // OTT별 파티 통계
        44 +          List<OttPartyStats> ottPartyStats = 
           + adminDashboardDao.getOttPartyStats().stream()
        45 +                  .map(m -> OttPartyStats.builder()
        46 +                          .ottName((String) m.get("ottName"))
        47 +                          
           + .partyCount(toLong(m.get("partyCount")))
        48 +                          
           + .activeCount(toLong(m.get("activeCount")))
        49 +                          .build())
        50 +                  .collect(Collectors.toList());
        51 +  
        52 +          // 최근 7일 매출
        53 +          List<DailyRevenue> dailyRevenues = 
           + adminDashboardDao.getDailyRevenues().stream()
        54 +                  .map(m -> DailyRevenue.builder()
        55 +                          .date((String) m.get("date"))
        56 +                          .amount(toLong(m.get("amount")))
        57 +                          .build())
        58 +                  .collect(Collectors.toList());
        59 +  
        60 +          // 최근 가입 회원
        61 +          List<RecentUser> recentUsers = 
           + adminDashboardDao.getRecentUsers().stream()
        62 +                  .map(m -> RecentUser.builder()
        63 +                          .odUserId((String) 
           + m.get("odUserId"))
        64 +                          .userName((String) 
           + m.get("userName"))
        65 +                          .userEmail((String) 
           + m.get("userEmail"))
        66 +                          .regDate((String) m.get("regDate"))
        67 +                          .build())
        68 +                  .collect(Collectors.toList());
        69 +  
        70 +          // 최근 결제 내역
        71 +          List<RecentPayment> recentPayments = 
           + adminDashboardDao.getRecentPayments().stream()
        72 +                  .map(m -> RecentPayment.builder()
        73 +                          
           + .paymentId(toLong(m.get("paymentId")))
        74 +                          .odUserId((String) 
           + m.get("odUserId"))
        75 +                          .amount(toLong(m.get("amount")))
        76 +                          .status((String) m.get("status"))
        77 +                          .paymentDate((String) 
           + m.get("paymentDate"))
        78 +                          .partyName((String) 
           + m.get("partyName"))
        79 +                          .build())
        80 +                  .collect(Collectors.toList());
        81 +  
        82 +          return DashboardStatsResponse.builder()
        83 +                  .totalRevenue(totalRevenue)
        84 +                  .activePartyCount(activePartyCount)
        85 +                  .totalPartyCount(totalPartyCount)
        86 +                  .totalUserCount(totalUserCount)
        87 +                  .todayNewUsers(todayNewUsers)
        88 +                  .thisMonthRevenue(thisMonthRevenue)
        89 +                  .recruitingPartyCount(recruitingPartyCount)
        90 +                  .pendingPaymentCount(pendingPaymentCount)
        91 +                  
           + .completedPaymentCount(completedPaymentCount)
        92 +                  
           + .thisMonthPaymentCount(thisMonthPaymentCount)
        93 +                  .ottPartyStats(ottPartyStats)
        94 +                  .dailyRevenues(dailyRevenues)
        95 +                  .recentUsers(recentUsers)
        96 +                  .recentPayments(recentPayments)
        97 +                  .build();
        98 +      }
        99 +  
       100 +      private long toLong(Object obj) {
       101 +          if (obj == null) return 0;
       102 +          if (obj instanceof Long) return (Long) obj;
       103 +          if (obj instanceof Integer) return ((Integer) 
           + obj).longValue();
       104 +          if (obj instanceof Number) return ((Number) 
           + obj).longValue();
       105 +          return 0;
       106 +      }
       107 +  }

● 백엔드 API 확장이 완료되었습니다. 이제 프론트엔드 대시보드 페이지를
  LandingPageT 스타일로 리디자인하겠습니다.

       241 +  export default function AdminDashboardPage() {
       242 +      const { stats, loading, error } = useAdminDashboard();
       243 +  
       244 +      if (loading) {
       245 +          return (

  변경 사항 요약

  백엔드 (4beans-moa-backend)

  1. DashboardStatsResponse.java - 응답 DTO 확장
  - 기존: totalRevenue, activePartyCount, totalPartyCount, totalUserCount
  - 추가: todayNewUsers, thisMonthRevenue, recruitingPartyCount,
  pendingPaymentCount, completedPaymentCount, thisMonthPaymentCount
  - 새 내부 클래스: OttPartyStats, DailyRevenue, RecentUser, RecentPayment

  2. AdminDashboardDao.java - 새로운 쿼리 메서드 추가
  - getTodayNewUsers(), getThisMonthRevenue(), getRecruitingPartyCount() 등
  - getOttPartyStats() - OTT 서비스별 파티 통계
  - getDailyRevenues() - 최근 7일 매출
  - getRecentUsers() - 최근 가입 회원 5명
  - getRecentPayments() - 최근 결제 내역 5건

  3. AdminDashboardMapper.xml - SQL 쿼리 추가
  4. AdminDashboardServiceImpl.java - 서비스 로직 업데이트

  프론트엔드 (4beans-moa-front)

  AdminDashboardPage.jsx - LandingPageT 스타일로 완전 리디자인

  주요 특징:
  - AnimatedGradient & GridPattern: 배경에 은은한 애니메이션 효과
  - 8개 통계 카드: 총 매출, 이번 달 매출, 총 회원, 활성 파티, 모집중 파티,
  결제 대기, 완료된 결제, 오늘 가입
  - Line 차트: 최근 7일 매출 추이 (기존 Bar → Line으로 변경)
  - Doughnut 차트: 파티 상태별 분포
  - OTT별 파티 현황: 프로그레스 바로 활성화율 시각화
  - 최근 가입 회원: 5명 표시
  - 최근 결제 내역: 5건 표시 (상태 배지 포함)
  - 빠른 작업 버튼: 회원 관리, 파티 목록, 블랙리스트, 공지사항, FAQ 관리,
  문의 관리
  - Framer Motion 애니메이션: 모든 요소에 순차적 등장 효과
  - 색상 스킴: #635bff (primary), #00d4ff (accent) - LandingPageT와 동일

> check error. 
org.springframework.jdbc.BadSqlGrammarException: 
### Error querying database.  Cause: java.sql.SQLSyntaxErrorException: 
Unknown column 'OD_USER_ID' in 'field list'
### The error may exist in file [C:\sol\React\4beans-moa-front\4beans-moa-ba
ckend\target\classes\sql\AdminDashboardMapper.xml]
### The error may involve defaultParameterMap
### The error occurred while setting parameters
### SQL: SELECT             OD_USER_ID as odUserId,             USER_NAME as
 userName,             USER_EMAIL as userEmail,             
DATE_FORMAT(REG_DATE, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') as regDate         FROM USERS
